<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: rgb(1, 1, 109); color: rgb(250, 94, 224); padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(252, 137, 233); color: rgb(1, 1, 109); }
        .notice-box { background-color: rgb(1, 1, 109); color: rgb(250, 94, 224); padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0; text-align: center; }
        .notice-box h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; }
        .notice-box p { margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.8; }
        .footer { background-color: rgb(1, 1, 109); color: rgb(250, 94, 224); padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Session Expired</h1>
            <p>Hello, <%= firstName %>!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Your session on Nana's Pourfection Hub has expired and you have been automatically logged out for your security.</p>

            <div class="notice-box">
                <h2><%= email %></h2>
                <p>⏱ Session Expired — You have been logged out</p>
            </div>

            <p>Sessions expire after a period of inactivity to keep your account safe, especially on shared devices.</p>
            <p>If you did not expect this or believe your account has been compromised, please contact our support team immediately. Otherwise, simply log back in to continue.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Nana's Pourfection Hub Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Nana's Pourfection Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>